Nsang Dilong a mụrụ (Bodi Nsang Dilung) n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ afọ 1994) bụ onye Cameroon na-eme ihe nkiri, onye ọrụ mmekọrịta ọha na eze na onye nlereanya
Ọ bụ onye mmeri nke mbipụta afọ 2011 nke Miss West Africa Cameroon Competition (MWACC). N'afọ 2015, ọ bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri na Fox Broadcasting Company
A mụrụ Nsang Dilong Bodi Nsang Dilung na Buea Cameroon, ọ bụ nwa afọ Kotto Barombi na Kumba na ọ nweghị ozi gbasara ụbọchị ọmụmụ ya, a mụrụ ya n'ihe dị ka afọ 1994
N'oge ọ nọ n'ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị, ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ na PCSS Buea ma gụchaa na PHS na Kumba
O nwere nzere bachelọ nke sayensị na Sociology n'afọ 2011 na Mahadum Buea

N'afọ 2011 ọ meriri asọmpi Miss West Africa Cameroon (MWACC). N'afọ 2013, ọ bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri nke Miss Cameroon Beauty Pageant, ọ na-eme na ihe nkiri dịka Whisper, Expression, ọ na'emekwa ihe nkiri na Zamba, usoro telivishọn na-enweta ihe nrite. N'afọ 2015, ọ bụ onye na-elekọta telivishọn na mmemme a na-akpọ African-focus show maka Fox Broadcasting Company (Fox 28).Mgbe e nyere ya onyinye ahụ, o kwuru
